Utterances.UttText: S: Gerry Cage is a 55 YOF with a history of hypertension who presents today after an episode of chest pain.

today after an episode of chest pain.

Utterances.UttText: She says 3 days ago she had sudden onset substernal midline chest pain that felt like "heaviness" while carrying heavy groceries.

Phrases.PhraseText: sudden onset substernal midline chest pain

Utterances.UttText: The pain didn't radiate anywhere and resolved spontaneously on its own after 5 minutes of rest.
She had associated faintness and shortness of breath at the time which also resolved with the rest.

Phrases.PhraseText: shortness of breath at the time

Utterances.UttText: States she has never felt this specific pain before but has previously experienced episodes of "twinges" in the chest during exertion.
